ğŸš€ Overview

CardioGuard AI is a machine-learning based web application that predicts the likelihood of heart disease using patient health metrics.
This project uses:

Logistic Regression (ML model)

StandardScaler (feature scaling)

Flask backend API

Responsive Frontend (HTML + CSS + JS)

The system takes user inputs (age, cholesterol, chest pain type, etc.), sends them to a Flask API, and returns:
âœ” Disease prediction (0 = No Disease, 1 = Disease)
âœ” Confidence score

